                    P = (((e x (c x d) x 30 x 10%) + (((i x j) x l x 8) x 10%)) x 12
                </h4>
                <h4 class="fs-14 fw-semibold mb-2">
                    P = (((0 x (0 x 0) x 30 x 10%) + (((0 x 0) x 0 x 8) x 10%)) x 12
                </h4>
