                    P = ((0 x 0 x 30 x 10%) + (0 x 0 x 8 x 10%)) x 12
                </h4>
                <h4 class="fs-14 fw-semibold mb-2">
                    P = ((0 x 10%) + (0 x 10%)) x 12
                </h4>
                <h4 class="fs-14 fw-semibold mb-2">
                    P = (0 + 0) x 12
                </h4>
                <h4 class="fs-14 fw-semibold mb-2">
                    P = 0 x 12
                </h4>
                <h4 class="fs-14 fw-semibold mb-2">
                    P = 0
                </h4>
            </div>
        </div>
